{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had blond hair and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the girls in the class actually raised her hand-- which was-- it was either courageous or dumb-- and asked Miss.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Arnold, well, how is it that that isn't always true?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because here, Thea Bloch-- that was me-- is sitting here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she is Jewish, and she has blond hair and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have dark hair and dark eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of others have as well dark hair and dark eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the woman was really dumbstruck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She started to stutter a little bit, the teacher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she, well, well, you have to realize when you look at Thea's hair very carefully, you will-- you will see that there is like dark shades underneath.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My hair wasn't bleached.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was natural.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were no dark shades underneath.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this is how she attempted to explain it away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, your-- your dark hair really have some golden light highlights when you look real close.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All-- all of you who have dark hair, you have some golden light highlights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how she explained it away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this is the kind of garbage, you know, that was fed to-- to the German children at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These are the children then who were sucked into the BDM, which was the girl's Hitler-- part of the Hitler Youth and the Hitler Youth, which was the boy's part of the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were constantly subjected to what those evil, ugly, sly, despicable Jews are up to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that you must have nothing-- that good Germans, have nothing to do with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those are the people that when the war started, they were like 20, 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
